+/* SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0+ WITH Linux-syscall-note */
+/*
+ * Author: Hanlu Li <lihanlu@loongson.cn>
+ *         Huacai Chen <chenhuacai@loongson.cn>
+ *
+ * Copyright (C) 2020-2021 Loongson Technology Corporation Limited
